        <Parent_String>megalithic chamber tombs [300005934], chamber tombs [300005935], tombs by form [300120617], tombs [300005926], funerary structures [300122208], ceremonial structures [300263489], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
